This is mirror of dvips/ from

    http://ftp.cs.stanford.edu/pub/dvips/dvips576.tar.gz

with changes to

    config.ps
    Makefile
    texc.lpro
    tex.lpro
    dvips.c
    loadfont.c

Installation:
1) download this to ~/dvips/ with name dvips and
   make as many copies as you use modes with names of modes
2) in each directory with name of mode edit Makefile to use
   name of corresponding mode instead of 'mode'
3) run make in each directory

==============================================================

